org.efaps.admin.datamodel

Class Attribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.efaps.admin.AbstractAdminObject
      • org.efaps.admin.datamodel.AbstractDataModelObject
        • org.efaps.admin.datamodel.Attribute
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, CacheObjectInterface

    public class Attribute
extends AbstractDataModelObject
    This is the class for the attribute description. The type description holds information about creation of a new instance of a attribute with default values.

        _id - id of the attribute
        _parentId - id of the parent type
        _name - name of the instance
        _sqlColNames - name of the SQL columns
        _sqlTable - table of this attribute
        _attributeType - type of this attribute
        _defaultValue - default value for this attribute
        _dimensionUUID - UUID of the Dimension
        Throws:
        EFapsException - on error while retrieving column information from database
